brewery.brewery_description: The largest brewery producing beer in Latvia. Cēsu alus has a variety of beer brands with Cēsu Premium being the flagship. Brūža is the 2nd largest line especially created by the Master Brewer Māris Grambergs. Cēsu Light is a small line for off-trade, and Pooka is a craft line for on-trade. New products are on the way each season, while Corona and Warsteiner are being distributed by Cēsu brewery logistics and sales teams. Dārza Sidrs, is the biggest locally produced cider line with white labeled sweeter selections and black labeled no added sugar tastes.

Something in my head, it won't switch off when I'm alone

Lord, beer me strength.

Blueberry-flavoured Fizz cider is a light alcoholic drink, produced on the basis of local apple wine. It is a purple-coloured drink with a light hint of wild blueberries that is refreshing in the winter time, reminding you of summer and just as nice and cooling during the warm summer days. It tastes best in good company!

Strawberry-flavoured effervescent Fizz Strawberry cider is produced on the basis of apple wine. This cider is a taste treat for everyone who appreciates sun-ripened fruits and values the natural flavour of a clear, light, and quality drink in the summer time. It also brings the summer to mind on a winter evening in front of the fireplace.
Enjoy with friends!
Traditional natural fermentation cider made with apple juice.
What happens when you take a good old style and add there some Mosaic hops in the dry hop? A great hoppy lager happens!
